iii) A representation of the  algebra constructed in this paper involves a central
charge which appears in the brackets of the supersymmetry generators with the superconformal ones
and is proportional to the (dimensionless) coupling constant  (see Appendix).
If one assumes that -particle -invariant model can be constructed along similar
lines, the central term is likely to have the form  (in this respect see also Ref. ).
Then, in order to preserve the algebraic structure, the large  limit is to be accompanied by
taking  to be small with  fixed.




